net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component

Class Table

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component.ComponentImpl
      • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component.Table
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<Component>, EventListener, LocaleContextSource, ColumnModelProvider, Component, ParentComponent, TableModelListener, Pageable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DataColumnTable

    public class Table
extends ComponentImpl
implements Pageable, TableModelListener, ColumnModelProvider, ParentComponent

    The Table handles a table of data. It uses a TableModel object for the data. It handles selection of columns, rows and cells.

    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)
